questions.explanation:
**Spring 既依賴注入方式：**

**1. Setter 注入 (setter injection)**
```java
@Component
public class UserService {
    private UserDao userDao;

    @Autowired
    public void setUserDao(UserDao userDao) {
        this.userDao = userDao;
    }
}
```

**2. 構造函數注入 (constructor injection) - 推薦**
```java
@Component
public class UserService {
    private final UserDao userDao;

    @Autowired
    public UserService(UserDao userDao) {
        this.userDao = userDao;
    }
}
```

**3. Field 注入 (field injection)**
```java
@Component
public class UserService {
    @Autowired
    private UserDao userDao;
}
```

**4. @Bean 方法注入**
```java
@Configuration
public class AppConfig {
    @Bean
    public UserService userService() {
        return new UserService(userDao());
    }
}
```

**優缺點對比：**
- Setter: 靈活，但可能set錯
- Constructor: 推薦，確保非null，可測試
- Field: 簡單，但難測試，難發現循環依賴

**面試點：** 構造函數注入既好處？

questions.codeExample:
// 三種依賴注入方式

// 1. Field 注入 (最簡單，但唔推薦)
public class UserService {
    @Autowired
    private UserDao userDao;

    @Autowired
    private OrderService orderService;
}

// 2. Setter 注入 (可選既依賴)
public class UserService {
    private UserDao userDao;

    @Autowired
    public void setUserDao(UserDao userDao) {
        this.userDao = userDao;
    }
}

// 3. Constructor 注入 (推薦)
public class UserService {
    private final UserDao userDao;
    private final OrderService orderService;

    public UserService(UserDao userDao, OrderService orderService) {
        this.userDao = userDao;
        this.orderService = orderService;
    }
}

// 4. @Bean 注入 (用於@Configuration類)
@Configuration
public class ServiceConfig {

    @Bean
    public UserService userService(UserDao userDao) {
        return new UserService(userDao);
    }
}

// Spring 會點選擇？
// 1. 先搵 Constructor (如果得一個constructor，@Autowired可省略)
// 2. 再搵 Setter (@Autowired)
// 3. 最後搵 Field

// Bean 生命周期示例

@Component
public class UserService implements InitializingBean, DisposableBean {

    public UserService() {
        System.out.println("1. 構造函數");
    }

    @Autowired
    private UserDao userDao;

    @PostConstruct
    public void init() {
        System.out.println("3. @PostConstruct");
    }

    @Override
    public void afterPropertiesSet() throws Exception {
        System.out.println("4. InitializingBean");
    }

    @Bean(initMethod = "customInit")
    public UserService userService() {
        return new UserService();
    }

    public void customInit() {
        System.out.println("5. @Bean initMethod");
    }

    @PreDestroy
    public void destroy() {
        System.out.println("6. @PreDestroy");
    }

    @Override
    public void destroyMethod() throws Exception {
        System.out.println("7. DisposableBean");
    }
}

// 執行順序:
// 構造函數 → @Autowired → @PostConstruct → afterPropertiesSet → customInit
// 銷毀時: @PreDestroy → destroyMethod

questions.explanation:
**Spring 既事務傳播行為：**

**7 種傳播行為：**

1. **REQUIRED (默認)** - 有事務加入，冇事務創建
```java
@Transactional
public void methodA() {
    methodB();  // 會加入 methodA 既事務
}
```

2. **REQUIRES_NEW** - 總是創建新事務
```java
@Transactional(propagation = REQUIRES_NEW)
public void methodB() {
    // 獨立既新事務
}
```

3. **SUPPORTS** - 有事務加入，冇事務以非事務運行

4. **NOT_SUPPORTED** - 以非事務運行

5. **MANDATORY** - 必須有事務，否則異常

6. **NEVER** - 必須冇事務，否則異常

7. **NESTED** - 嵌套事務 (Savepoint)
```java
@Transactional(propagation = NESTED)
public void methodB() {
    // 如果 support 既事務入面，會用 Savepoint
}
```

**面試點：** REQUIRED vs REQUIRES_NEW 既分別？

questions.codeExample:
// 事務傳播行為示例

// REQUIRED (常用)
@Transactional
public void methodA() {
    // 有事務
    userDao.save(user);
    orderService.saveOrder();  // 會用同一事務
}

// REQUIRES_NEW (日誌記錄常用)
@Transactional
public void methodA() {
    userDao.save(user);
    logService.saveLog();  // 獨立事務，即使fail唔影響methodA
}

@Transactional(propagation = Propagation.REQUIRES_NEW)
public void saveLog() {
    // 總係開新事務
    // 如果fail，只影響自己
}

// NESTED (savepoint)
@Transactional
public void methodA() {
    try {
        userDao.save(user);  // savepoint 1
        orderService.saveOrder();  // savepoint 2
    } catch (Exception e) {
        // 可以只回滾部分
    }
}

// 查看當前事務
@Transactional
public void methodA() {
    TransactionStatus status = TransactionSynchronizationManager
        .getTransactionStatus();
    System.out.println(status.isNewTransaction());
}

questions.explanation:
Spring Boot自動配置原理：

**核心注解：**
```java
@SpringBootApplication
// 等價於：
@Configuration  // 標記為配置類
@EnableAutoConfiguration  // 啟用自動配置
@ComponentScan  // 包掃描
```

**@EnableAutoConfiguration：**
```java
@Target(ElementType.TYPE)
@Retention(RetentionPolicy.RUNTIME)
@Import(AutoConfigurationImportSelector.class)
public @interface EnableAutoConfiguration {
    String[] exclude() default {};
    String[] excludeName() default {};
}
```

**自動配置流程：**
```
1. @SpringBootApplication 觸發

2. @EnableAutoConfiguration
   └─ AutoConfigurationImportSelector

3. 掃描 META-INF/spring.factories
   └─ org.springframework.boot.autoconfigure.EnableAutoConfiguration

4. 加載候選配置類

5. @Conditional 過濾
   └─ @ConditionalOnClass  class存在才加載
   └─ @ConditionalOnBean  bean不存在才加載
   └─ @ConditionalOnProperty  配置存在才加載

6. 實例化並註冊Bean
```

**面試點：** 如何自定義自動配置？創建@Configuration類，用@Conditional注解condition，然後在spring.factories中註冊。

questions.codeExample:
// 自定義自動配置
package com.example.autoconfigure;

@Configuration
@ConditionalOnClass(MyService.class)  // class存在才加載
@ConditionalOnProperty(prefix = "my", name = "enabled", 
                       havingValue = "true", 
                       matchIfMissing = false)
@EnableConfigurationProperties(MyProperties.class)
public class MyAutoConfiguration {

    @Bean
    @ConditionalOnMissingBean  // 不存在才創建
    public MyService myService(MyProperties props) {
        return new MyService(props);
    }
}

// 配置屬性類
@ConfigurationProperties(prefix = "my")
@Data
public class MyProperties {
    private String name = "default";
    private int timeout = 3000;
}

// 註冊：META-INF/spring.factories
org.springframework.boot.autoconfigure.EnableAutoConfiguration=\
com.example.autoconfigure.MyAutoConfiguration

// 使用
// application.yml:
// my:
//   enabled: true
//   name: myapp

-- 查看當前會話隔離級別
